<br>
&quot;Blessed Fishing Pole, cost to make at 200 skill 125 - 500 plat depending if you can forage or not. Time to make: 30-60 minutes if you forage components yourself, 15 minutes if you buy them in Bazaar; priced accordingly as above. Price in bazaar 1500 - 2500 plat.&quot;<br>
